Noteworthy changes in version 0.8.4 (2004-05-07)
------------------------------------------------

* Allow more simultaneous connections and fail only temporary if we
  can't allocate a buffer anymore.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.8.3 (2004-03-31)
------------------------------------------------

* Fail gracefully on transient errors from MTAs.  This is especially
  required if the MTA is temporary under a high load and won't accept
  new data.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.8.0
-----------------------------------

* Add a manual in HTML and PS.
* Add option --inner-net


Noteworthy changes in version 0.5.3
-----------------------------------

* Fixed a race condition.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.5.3
-----------------------------------

* Add a few other checks to the make check target.

* Add a few X-Geam-Comment: header

